No. 590,

Mise.

Ashby v. Virginia. Robert Y. Button, Attorney General of Virginia, R. D. Mcll-waine III, First Assistant Attorney General, and Charles Shepherd Cox, Jr., Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Sup. Ct. App. Va. Certiorari denied. Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted.
